(5291, 1, '2014-09-10 03:52:24', '2014-09-10 03:52:24', '<p>Kim Hyun Joong singing Because I''m Stupid live at Goodbye Yoon Ji Hoon GBYJH fanmeeting. Song is from SS501 Boys Over Flowers and is performed on March 31, 2009 (31.03.09). Please note, this is not the actual recording of the performance of the song because Kim Hyun Joong messed up on several occasions (i.e. his que was off) and the company that released this video on DVD edited it before releasing it. Basically, the studio put the sound of the crowds in with the album/studio recording of this song instead. Please see the real version in the video response to see the difference (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7Cbm...). I''ve added English subtitles. Enjoy.</p>', 'Kim Hyun Joong - Because I''m Stupid (Live Goodbye Yoon Ji Hoon GBYJH fanmeeting) W/ English Subs', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'kim-hyun-joong-because-im-stupid-live-goodbye-yoon-ji-hoon-gbyjh-fanmeeting-w-english-subs', '', '', '2014-09-10 03:52:24', '2014-09-10 03:52:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/gv/2014/09/10/kim-hyun-joong-because-im-stupid-live-goodbye-yoon-ji-hoon-gbyjh-fanmeeting-w-english-subs/', 0, 'post', '', 0),
